results.title: Marvel Rivals Infinity Comic (2024) #9
results.description: BETRAYAL! Ultron has taken control of Arakko, Krakoa’s sister nation, and hacked its portals to invade the island of Krakoa! While the inhabitants of the island battle against his army of sentries, Ultron has taken over The Cradle and possesses Cerebro! And whoever controls Cerebro…controls all mutants in the multiverse! The chance of this grim reality does not sit well with Emma Frost, as she leads a group of heroes to destroy Cerebro before Ultron gains complete control over mutantkind!

results.title: Marvel Rivals Infinity Comic (2024) #7
results.description: WELCOME TO THE HELLFIRE GALA!!! The island of Krakoa is the home nation for mutants on Earth — as well as the venue for the best party ever…the Hellfire Gala! The celebration has been crashed by an army of Ultron sentries, and it’s up to the partygoers to save the island! Leader of the mutant inhabitants, Emma Frost, spearheads the fight alongside Psylocke, Magik and Storm! Will Krakoa prevail in saving itself from robotic dominion, or will its guests fail to help their mutant allies? And WHERE is Ultron???
